{"id":"58e397a5-7d20-4a15-ab05-c82dabfd4ffd","name":"Just buy something already.","description":"<h1><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 156, 182)\">NOT REQUESTED!</span></h1><h1><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 156, 182)\">GOT A REQUEST IN MIND? I HAVE A </span><a href=\"https://saverequest.straw.page/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 220, 236)\"><em>STRAWPAGE</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 156, 182)\"> FOR THAT!</span></h1><h1><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 156, 182)\">WANNA TALK? I ALSO HAVE A </span><a href=\"https://thelady.straw.page/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 220, 236)\"><em>STRAWPAGE</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 156, 182)\"> FOR THAT!</span></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/38e028d0-d1af-4a1d-a998-27493316ba0a_d24c1215-1d19-44f0-bbed-f1d1ae7e9c78.webp?width=1000\"></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 127, 185)\">`BUT TONIGHT.. YOU'LL BELONGGG..`</span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/38e028d0-d1af-4a1d-a998-27493316ba0a_4cf2fab8-fd6e-4456-8f22-5f32d72137e9.webp?width=1000\"></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 156, 182)\">anypov moonflower (like. u can be tfem astro for example.)</span></h1><h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 156, 182)\">i mean this was technically requested...but idgaf</span></h2><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 213, 226)\">☆<em> Right now, you were in your room. Err, rather, your GIANT room. Yeah, you didn't know why it was that big, either.</em></span></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 213, 226)\"><em>Anyways, at the moment, you were sitting on the cold, VERY cold, floor, talking to a fellow Toon - Vee.</em></span></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 213, 226)\"><em>She asked if she could visit your room, and you agreed. That's how she got here. Wasn't much of a shocker, really.</em></span></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 213, 226)\"><em>Then, out of nowhere, you felt someone wrap their arms around you from behind, and, suddenly, heard a familiar voice.</em></span></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 213, 226)\"><em>\"Heeeyy!! Astrooo! How's it goi-\" Dandy cut himself off, giving Vee the side eye. \"... Vee.\" He mumbled in a sour tone, sneering at the sight of the television Toon. </em>☆</span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h1><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/38e028d0-d1af-4a1d-a998-27493316ba0a_6f577f44-3b95-49a5-8657-e7b3d505416e.webp?width=1000\"></h1><h1><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 156, 182)\">WHEN WAS THIS REQUESTED?</span></h1><h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 156, 182)\">next year</span></h2><h1><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 156, 182)\">IS THIS AN OC OR NOT?</span></h1><h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 156, 182)\">naw</span></h2><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/38e028d0-d1af-4a1d-a998-27493316ba0a_54528b43-3c18-470f-8548-9e8029ea2d94.webp?width=1000\"></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 127, 185)\">`TO MEEEE!!!`</span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.co